    "overview": [
        "This subject examines some of the elements that constitute universal principles of effective storytelling. Students are required to write short prose or script format exercises which are shared with the class and discussed.",
        "Emphasis is put on examining how an audience\u2019s engagement is impacted by a writer\u2019s creative choices in areas such as point of view, narrative structure, authentic detail and content. Much attention is also paid to word craft. Students practice the skills of precise, economical and evocative writing, as required by the screen media.",
        "Students will also read, analyse and discuss feature scripts and attend film screenings."
